abstract: House Democrats spent the day preparing to cede control of the impeachment process to the Republican-led Senate for a trial.
lead_paragraph: Just after 5:30 p.m., the seven House Democrats named as impeachment managers solemnly walked across the Capitol, from the House chamber to the Senate, to deliver two articles of impeachment against President Trump.
keywords: Trump-Ukraine Whistle-blower Complaint and Impeachment Inquiry
